@startuml smc_client_management

title SMC Client Management - Singleton Pattern

' Styling
skinparam class {
    BackgroundColor<<Singleton>> LightYellow
    BorderColor<<Singleton>> Orange
    BackgroundColor<<Entity>> LightBlue
    BorderColor<<Entity>> Blue
}

skinparam stereotypeCBackgroundColor YellowGreen

' External dependency
package "internal/sdk/auth" {
    class Auth <<external>> {
    }
}

' Main entities
package "internal/smc" {

    class LogContext <<Entity>> {
        -ctx: context.Context
        -mgtServerId: string
        __
        +Context(): context.Context
        +WithField(key string, value interface{}): context.Context
        +WithFields(fields map[string]interface{}): context.Context
        +Debug(msg string, additionalFields ...map[string]interface{}): void
        +Info(msg string, additionalFields ...map[string]interface{}): void
        +Warn(msg string, additionalFields ...map[string]interface{}): void
        +Error(msg string, additionalFields ...map[string]interface{}): void
        +Trace(msg string, additionalFields ...map[string]interface{}): void
    }

    class Client <<Entity>> {
        +URL: string
        +APIKey: string
        +VerifySSL: bool
        +Token: string
        +HTTPClient: *http.Client
        +APIVersion: string
        +Auth: *sdk_auth.Auth
        +UseAuthHeader: bool
        +MgtServerId: string
        +SmcContext: *LogContext
        __
        +GetLogContext(): *LogContext
        +UpdateLogContext(ctx context.Context, mgtServerId string): void
    }

    class ClientManager <<Singleton>> {
        -clients: map[string]*Client
        -lock: sync.RWMutex
        __
        +GetClient(mgtServerId string): (*Client, error)
        +AddClient(mgtServerId string, client *Client): error
        +RemoveClient(mgtServerId string): void
        +HasClient(mgtServerId string): bool
        +ListClients(): []string
        +Clear(): void
    }

    class "Global Variables" as GlobalVars <<utility>> {
        {static} -managerInstance: *ClientManager
        __
        {static} +GetClientManager(): *ClientManager
    }
}

' Relationships
ClientManager "1" *-- "0..*" Client : manages >
Client --> Auth : uses >
Client *-- "1" LogContext : contains >
GlobalVars ..> ClientManager : creates/returns
GlobalVars : <<singleton pattern>>

' Notes
note right of ClientManager
  **Thread-Safe Singleton**
  - Uses sync.RWMutex for concurrent access
  - Directly initialized at package startup
  - Manages multiple SMC clients by MgtServerId

  **Note**: Multiple clients not yet fully supported,
  but prevents re-login by checking existing sessions
end note

note right of Client
  **SMC API Client**
  Represents an authenticated connection
  to a Stonesoft Management Center (SMC)

  MgtServerId identifies which SMC deployment
  this client is connected to
end note

note bottom of GlobalVars
  **Singleton Initialization**
  managerInstance is directly initialized
  as a package variable with an empty
  clients map at startup
end note

@enduml

